Maze

Class Maze_Build

  • java.lang.Object
    • Maze.Maze_Build
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Maze

    public class Maze_Build
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for the creation of a random Maze. The maze is square and of odd size.
